title: Garrett Wilson Joins The Show
description:
Field, Sam, Diana, Tannebaum, and Miller discuss Travon Walker possibly going #1, Jimmy G and Deebo’s future on the 49ers, if any WRs in this draft are worth trading up for, and Ohio State’s Garrett Wilson joins the show.
